@host = http://localhost:9090
@mediaId = 1
@token = <token-from-login>
@otherToken = <other-user-token>

### Submit a formal video analysis task
POST {{host}}/media/analyze/{{mediaId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "goal": "Summarize the core ideas of this video and return structured conclusions with evidence."
}

### Duplicate submission check
POST {{host}}/media/analyze/{{mediaId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "goal": "Summarize the core ideas of this video."
}

### Missing token should return 401
POST {{host}}/media/analyze/{{mediaId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "goal": "This request should return 401 because Authorization is missing."
}

### Permission check: use a token for a user that does not own the media
POST {{host}}/media/analyze/{{mediaId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{otherToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "goal": "This request should return 403 if the media belongs to another user."
}

### userId in query/body is ignored by the formal endpoint
POST {{host}}/media/analyze/{{mediaId}}?userId=999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 999,
  "goal": "The server should use Authorization token user, not this forged userId."
}

### Existing debug endpoint is still available
GET {{host}}/debug/ai?id={{mediaId}}&goal=Debug analysis task
